[0m[49m[39m  145, 145[0m:[39m[49m         G -->|Query Patient Data| H[HealthLake\nFHIR Store]
[0m[49m[39m  146, 146[0m:[39m[49m         G -->|Historical Features| I[S3 Feature Store\nParquet]
