[0m[49m[39m  157, 157[0m:[39m[49m         L -->|High Risk| M[SNS\nCare Team Alert]
[0m[49m[39m  158, 158[0m:[39m[49m         L -->|All Scores| N[DynamoDB\nRisk Score Store]
[0m[49m[39m  159, 159[0m:[39m[49m         L -->|Dashboard| O[QuickSight\nReadmission Analytics]
